@startuml
[*] --> Idle

Idle --> DealerRegistration : introduce new dealer
DealerRegistration --> Registered : registration successful

Registered --> RequestProduct : product out of stock
RequestProduct --> SendingRequest : request sent to dealer

SendingRequest --> ReceivedProducts : products received from dealer

ReceivedProducts --> UpdateDatabase : shipment details updated
UpdateDatabase --> Idle : database updated

@enduml
